  "title": "torch.Tensor.index_add_ — PyTorch 2.10 documentation",
  "description": "Accumulate the elements ofalphatimessourceinto theselftensor by adding to the indices in the order given inindex. For example,\nifdim==0,index[i]==j, andalpha=-1, then theith row ofsourceis subtracted from thejth row ofself.",
